# Familiars
Arctic Fox	> Use Fox		SOURCEPAGE:p.10
#Use the statistics for a fox (
Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 3
112).
The greatest difference between a typical fox and an arctic fox
that the white fur of an arctic fox allows it to better blend in
with its snowy environment. An arctic fox receives a +4 racial
bonus on Stealth checks attempted while in snow.
	BONUS:SITUATION|Stealth=in snow|4
