Ermine		SOURCEPAGE:p.10
Use the statistics for a weasel (Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 133).
While an ermine is a type of weasel, this specimen has white
fur that allows it to blend into snowy surroundings. An ermine
receives a +4 racial bonus on Stealth checks attempted while
in snow.
	BONUS:SITUATION|Stealth=in snow|4

