Snowy Owl	SOURCEPAGE:p.1
Use the statistics for an owl (Bestiary 132). A snowy owl has
white feathers that allow it to blend in with its surroundings
during winter. A snowy owl receives a +4 racial bonus on
Stealth checks attempted while in snow.
	BONUS:SITUATION|Stealth=in snow|4
